    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the juice of the<strong> orange halves</strong> with your <strong>miso paste</strong>, <strong>rice vinegar</strong>, 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> in a small bowl – this is your <strong>orange-miso dressing</strong></p>",
