    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel the <strong>remaining orange[s]</strong> and slice finely</p><p>Cut your <strong>sugar snap peas </strong>in half lengthways</p><p>Trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p><p>Chop your <strong>coriander</strong> roughly, including the stalks</p>",
