    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>avocado[s]</strong><span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>in half lengthways, around the <strong>stone[s]</strong></p><p>Remove the <strong>stone[s]</strong> using a spoon, then scoop out the <strong>avocado flesh</strong> and slice finely</p>",
