    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Add the <strong>salad</strong>, <strong>cooked quinoa </strong>(still steaming hot? Rinse it under cold water!), <strong>sliced spring onion</strong>, <strong>sugar snap peas</strong> and <strong>coriander</strong> to a large bowl</p><p>Add most of the <strong>orange-miso dressing</strong> (save the rest for later!) and give it a gentle mix up – this is your<strong> quinoa salad</strong></p>",
