    {
      "instruction": "<p>Divide the<strong> quinoa salad</strong> between plates</p><p>Top with the <strong>cooked salmon</strong>,<strong> orange slices </strong>and the <strong>sliced avocado</strong></p><p>Drizzle over the <strong>remaining orange-miso dressing</strong> and garnish with your <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>sesame seeds</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
